<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whereas-conj">whereas <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌweər'æz/    美 /ˌwer'æz/  </p>
<p>[引导进行对比、 对照的从句]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>然而；反之：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He must be about sixty, whereas his wife looks about thirty. 
他肯定六十岁左右，而他妻子看起来只有大约三十岁。</p></div></div>